    "spell": {
        "name": "Elemental Sheath",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "text": "You coat yourself in nature\u2019s power. Choose air, earth, fire, metal, water, or wood; the spell gains that trait. You become completely covered by armor formed from that element, gaining a +1 circumstance bonus to AC and resistance 5 to two types of damage based on the element you choose.   \n  \n**Air** bludgeoning and electricity; **Earth** bludgeoning and poison; **Fire** fire and slashing; **Metal** acid and slashing; **Water** cold and piercing; **Wood** piercing and void.",
        "subtype": "spell",
        "spell_type": "focus",
        "rank": 4,
